                     <interp inst="t18130602-58-person511" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . You parted with three boxes and a watch to Mr. Hanley - A. I did, and the thing I now produce are the things that I received from Mr. Hanley.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18130602-58-person512">
                  Harry 
                  Adkins
               <interp inst="t18130602-58-person512" type="surname" value="Adkins"></interp>
