                  </persName>
            . The other things I have in my custody.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you go to Levy's house - A. I did, at Poplar. I found 
               <persName id="t18130602-58-person513">
                  Joseph 
                  Levy
               <interp inst="t18130602-58-person513" type="surname" value="Levy"></interp>
