             tried to unclasp it; he took the pocket-book again.</p>
               <p>Mr. 
               <persName id="t18130602-58-person524">Knapp, Q.</persName>
             to Beckitt. I asked you particular about a bando - A. I now produce it; I had not got it then. I received it of 
               <persName id="t18130602-58-person525">
